    "date": "2020-04-06T19:06:45Z",
    "text": "Interim Stay Authority To Protect Whistleblowers Act\n\nThis bill authorizes the general counsel of the Merit Systems Protection Board to temporarily act as a member of the board when dealing with matters related to the staying of certain personnel actions, and it authorizes a single member of the board to carry out certain board duties in the event of a lack of quorum."
